96
00:07:48,453 --> 00:07:49,547
Inspecteurs.

97
00:07:49,573 --> 00:07:51,520
Ya toute une foule dehors.

98
00:07:52,962 --> 00:07:55,190
Matt Spicer. Adam Kurzbard.

99
